Scalextreme nodejs APM plugin

Install:
    npm install git+https://github.com/scalextremeinc/scalex-apm-node.git

Import plugin:
    require('scalex-apm-plugin');

Configure and run:
    export SCALEX_COLLECTOR_URL=http://example.com/collector/transaction
    export SCALEX_CUSTOMER=test
    export SCALEX_APP=server
    export SCALEX_UPLOAD_INTERVAL=5000
    export SCALEX_APM_LOG_LEVEL=DEBUG
    node server.js
